<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: 「Jade Immortal」XuanDan Zi -->
  <RI_Storytellers_ImmortalDanTzu.label>「玉仙」玄丹子</RI_Storytellers_ImmortalDanTzu.label>
  <!-- EN: XuanDan Zi is one of the five Celestial Masters who survived the Founder's War. After traveling the world, he attained enlightenment and became an Immortal.\n\nHe is a compassionate and kind storyteller. He will offer you a more relaxed gaming experience, ensuring your faction prospers. However, during this time, he will also draw more attention to your colony from others. -->
  <RI_Storytellers_ImmortalDanTzu.description>玄丹子是方圆战争中存活的五位龙师之一，后来得道飞升，成为玉仙。\n\n他是仁慈而良善的故事讲述者，会给你较为放松的游戏体验，令你的殖民地风调雨顺，在这期间，他也会让你的殖民地受到更多乞讨者的关注。</RI_Storytellers_ImmortalDanTzu.description>
  
</LanguageData>